    About this item

    • Includes 10 charming Barbie watch faces to match your child’s personality
    • Features 6 interactive games that entertain while promoting learning
    • Built-in selfie and video camera for capturing magical Barbie moments
    • Step tracker and calorie counter to encourage an active lifestyle
    • Adjustable printed silicone strap with colorful Barbie designs, fitting wrist sizes from 5.5" to 8.0"

    Description

    Let your child immerse themselves in the enchanting world of Barbie with the Barbie Kids Smart Watch. This interactive smartwatch combines style, fun, and practicality with 10 captivating Barbie-themed watch faces, letting kids showcase their favorite Barbie moments. The watch is designed to engage young minds with 6 built-in games that provide fun and learning. A selfie and video camera captures memorable adventures, while the step tracker and calorie counter encourage an active and healthy lifestyle. Parents can appreciate features like the alarm, timer, and stopwatch, which help teach kids time management in an enjoyable way. With its vibrant printed silicone strap and adjustable fit for wrist sizes 5.5" to 8.0", this smartwatch is perfect for kids on the move. The Barbie Kids Smart Watch is an ideal companion for play, learning, and self-expression.
